    <title>WebSocket 从0开发</title>
    <link href="https://shuai4983958.github.io/blogShuai.github.io/2018/04/17/hello-world/"/>
    <id>https://shuai4983958.github.io/blogShuai.github.io/2018/04/17/hello-world/</id>
    <published>2018-04-17T04:06:20.000Z</published>
    <updated>2018-04-18T12:28:20.000Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>&emsp;&emsp;在聊websoket之前呢！我们先聊聊http，几大必须要知道的点分享一下：<br>&emsp;&emsp;Welcome to <a href="/blogShuai.github.io/2018/04/18/HTTP协议/">HTTP协议</a>! </p><h2 id="关于WebSocket的基础知识，"><a href="#关于WebSocket的基础知识，" class="headerlink" title="关于WebSocket的基础知识，"></a>关于WebSocket的基础知识，</h2><p>&emsp;&emsp;可以参考<a href="http://www.ruanyifeng.com/blog/2017/05/websocket.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">阮一峰的博客</a>不过稍微重要的几点我们可以拿出来重点交流一下：</p><ul><li><p>WebSocket的优势总结：</p><ul><li>1、（双向通信）服务器可以主动向客户端推送信息，客户端也可以主动向服务器发送信息</li><li>2、与http协议类似，都是建立在tcp传输协议之上</li><li>3、与服务器通信，url的协议标识符是ws，加密的话则为wss</li><li>4、客户端通过websocket协议可以与任意服务器通信，没有同源限制。<figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">项目采用的websocket协议与服务器端通信的列子：</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span>(<span class="keyword">typeof</span> WebSocket !== <span class="string">'function'</span>)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">          <span class="built_in">console</span>.log(<span class="string">'不支持websocket'</span>)</span><br><span class="line">          <span class="comment">//判断浏览器是否支持websocket</span></span><br><span class="line">   &#125;<span class="keyword">else</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">       <span class="keyword">let</span>  ws = <span class="keyword">new</span> WebSocket(<span class="string">`ws://chat.willclass.com?secret=89414b156e300f169462647ed7106d326a8d641e&amp;roomId=<span class="subst">$&#123;classroomId&#125;</span><span class="subst">$&#123;data.courseId&#125;</span>&amp;cid=<span class="subst">$&#123;<span class="built_in">window</span>.userId&#125;</span>`</span>);</span><br><span class="line">        ws.onmessage = <span class="keyword">this</span>.getmsg;</span><br><span class="line">        ws.onclose = <span class="keyword">this</span>.reConnect</span><br><span class="line">        ws.onerror = <span class="keyword">this</span>.reConnect</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul></li><li><p>无序列表2 </p><ul><li>无序列表2.1 <ul><li>列表内容 </li><li>列表内容</li></ul></li></ul></li></ul><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo new <span class="string">"My New Post"</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>More info: <a href="https://hexo.io/docs/writing.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Writing</a></p><h3 id="Run-server"><a href="#Run-server" class="headerlink" title="Run server"></a>Run server</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo server</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>More info: <a href="https://hexo.io/docs/server.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Server</a></p><h3 id="Generate-static-files"><a href="#Generate-static-files" class="headerlink" title="Generate static files"></a>Generate static files</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo generate</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>More info: <a href="https://hexo.io/docs/generating.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Generating</a></p><h3 id="Deploy-to-remote-sites"><a href="#Deploy-to-remote-sites" class="headerlink" title="Deploy to remote sites"></a>Deploy to remote sites</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo deploy</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>More info: <a href="https://hexo.io/docs/deployment.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Deployment</a></p>]]></content>
    
